p1 -> p2: storage foundation
p1 -> p5: Rust toolchain

p2 -> p3: Cache API + OPFS
p2 -> p6: IDB + OPFS
p2 -> p10: IDB event queue

p3 -> p4: SW lifecycle
p3 -> p8: Cache API

p4 -> p8: manifest diff
p4 -> p9: version detection

p5 -> p6: WASM binary

p3 -> p7: SW registration
p6 -> p7: inference path

p7 -> p9: engine readiness
p7 -> p11: health API

p8 -> p9: artifact cache

p9 -> p11: swap metrics
p10 -> p11: uplink metrics
